The Surface Operations menu has the following selections:

Make RTT_MC Interface File
   Used to write the results of a reconstruction to a set of two interface files for the rtt_MC process.

Shoot Ray Dialog
   Displays a dialog to allow the user to fire individual rays at the reconstructed geometry in the reconstruction view dialog.

Display Particle Paths
   This option will display neutron, photon, and beam line tracks from a track file generated by a previous rtt_MC process.
